OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud will soon break up
OL,6,Fto give a mostly fine day with bright
OL,7,For sunny spells. Feeling very warm and
OL,8,Fmuggy. Light winds. Chance of isolated
OL,9,Fthunderstorms from late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud and showers clear
OL,12,Feastwards giving a dry and settled
OL,13,Fevening. Winds are light but breezy
OL,14,Falong the coast. Overnight
OL,15,Ftemperatures remaining warm and muggy.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FMostly fine with some
OL,18,Fsunshine. Turning very warm or locally
OL,19,Fhot, and feeling humid. Winds remain
OL,20,Flight and variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
