OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FChangeable on Saturday with some
OL,7,Fspells and showers moving erratically
OL,8,Feastwards. Perhaps drier with warm
OL,9,Fsunny spells Sunday and Monday with
OL,10,Ftemperatures climbing.
